p.d: A 24-year-old man is found strangled. In his mouth is a disc featuring a four-leaf clover. This is in fact a gaming chip from the Villa Jaume, today a hotel but formerly a casino in the 1960s. Directed by: Jérôme Navarro (season 2, France, 2016) Screenplay: Franck Calderon, Nicole Jamet, Dominique Lancelot Cast: Vanessa David (Margot Laurent), Julien Baumgartner (Arthur du Plessis), Christian Rauth (Stavros), Nathalie Blanc (the public prosecutor), Maud Forget (Garnier) Genre: detective
